    <entry>
      <title>VPS一键dd纯净系统并更改秘钥登录</title>
      <link href="/2022/02/02/vps-centos/"/>
      <url>/2022/02/02/vps-centos/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>一些VPS商家默认配置非纯净系统，为用户使用带来不便。本文以CentOS为例，记录使用一键脚本重装纯净系统，并设置仅密钥登录防止暴力破解。</p></blockquote><h2 id="1-重装系统"><a href="#1-重装系统" class="headerlink" title="1.重装系统"></a>1.重装系统</h2><p>使用一键网络重装系统脚本，可以通过Internet重新安装Linux和Windows以及常见的操作系统。<br>具体操作方法如下：<br>CentOS系统</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum update -y</span><br><span class="line">yum install -y xz openssl gawk file</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下载脚本(root用户)</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 别人备份的镜像</span></span><br><span class="line">wget http://shell.p1e.cn/reinstall/dd.sh &amp;&amp; chmod +x dd.sh &amp;&amp; ./dd.sh</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 原版地址</span></span><br><span class="line">wget --no-check-certificate -qO ~/Network-Reinstall-System-Modify.sh &#x27;https://www.cxthhhhh.com/tech-tools/Network-Reinstall-System-Modify/Network-Reinstall-System-Modify.sh&#x27; &amp;&amp; chmod a+x ~/Network-Reinstall-System-Modify.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装Linux系统</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 一键网络重装纯净CentOS 7</span></span><br><span class="line">bash ~/Network-Reinstall-System-Modify.sh -CentOS_7</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>默认密码：cxthhhhh.com<br>本文仅列出CentOS 7安装方法，更多脚本使用方法参考：<a href="https://www.cxthhhhh.com/network-reinstall-system-modify">https://www.cxthhhhh.com/network-reinstall-system-modify</a></p><h2 id="2-修改密码"><a href="#2-修改密码" class="headerlink" title="2.修改密码"></a>2.修改密码</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">passwd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意：输入密码不会显示，输入完毕直接回车即可。</p><h2 id="3-同步时间"><a href="#3-同步时间" class="headerlink" title="3.同步时间"></a>3.同步时间</h2><h3 id="3-1查看时间"><a href="#3-1查看时间" class="headerlink" title="3.1查看时间"></a>3.1查看时间</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">date -R</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-2设置时区为北京时间"><a href="#3-2设置时区为北京时间" class="headerlink" title="3.2设置时区为北京时间"></a>3.2设置时区为北京时间</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rm -rf /etc/localtime</span><br><span class="line">ln -s /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai /etc/localtime</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-3NTP-同步时间协议"><a href="#3-3NTP-同步时间协议" class="headerlink" title="3.3NTP 同步时间协议"></a>3.3NTP 同步时间协议</h3><p>CentOS系统</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install ntp ntpdate -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接下来我们需要先停止 NTP 服务器，再更新时间。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">service ntpd stop #停止 ntp 服务</span><br><span class="line">ntpdate us.pool.ntp.org #同步 ntp 时间</span><br><span class="line">service ntpd start #启动 ntp 服务</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>对完时间后，我们需要将当前时间和日期写入BIOS，避免重启后失效，命令如下：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hwclock -w</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4-密钥登录"><a href="#4-密钥登录" class="headerlink" title="4.密钥登录"></a>4.密钥登录</h2><h3 id="4-1生成密钥对"><a href="#4-1生成密钥对" class="headerlink" title="4.1生成密钥对"></a>4.1生成密钥对</h3><p>在远端VPS上执行如下命令，之后将私钥<code>id_rsa</code>文件下载到本地。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-2安装公钥"><a href="#4-2安装公钥" class="headerlink" title="4.2安装公钥"></a>4.2安装公钥</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd .ssh/ </span><br><span class="line">cat id_rsa.pub &gt;&gt; authorized_keys #将公钥写入到 authorized_keys 文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-3修改权限"><a href="#4-3修改权限" class="headerlink" title="4.3修改权限"></a>4.3修改权限</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chmod 600 authorized_keys</span><br><span class="line">chmod 700 ~/.ssh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-4修改-sshd-配置文件"><a href="#4-4修改-sshd-配置文件" class="headerlink" title="4.4修改 sshd 配置文件"></a>4.4修改 sshd 配置文件</h3><p>执行<code>vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config</code> 找到以下参数进行更改：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">RSAAuthentication yes</span><br><span class="line">PubkeyAuthentication yes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重启 sshd 服务</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">service sshd restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-5禁用密码登录"><a href="#4-5禁用密码登录" class="headerlink" title="4.5禁用密码登录"></a>4.5禁用密码登录</h3><p>在你确认密钥能成功登录后，如果需要禁用密码登录，请更改以下参数：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">PasswordAuthentication no</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重启 sshd 服务</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">service sshd restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
