    <entry>
      <title>群晖搭建Alist网盘列表教程</title>
      <link href="/2022/01/22/alist/"/>
      <url>/2022/01/22/alist/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>Alist是一款支持本地存储、阿里云盘、天翼云盘、蓝奏云等多种存储的目录文件列表程序，支持 web 浏览与 webdav，完美解决了单个网盘容量不足、网盘数量太多不方便管理与使用的痛点。</p></blockquote><p>项目地址：<a href="https://github.com/Xhofe/alist">https://github.com/Xhofe/alist</a></p><p>官方文档：<a href="https://alist-doc.nn.ci/docs/intro">https://alist-doc.nn.ci/docs/intro</a></p><p>作者博客：<a href="https://www.nn.ci/archives/alist.html">https://www.nn.ci/archives/alist.html</a></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/holob/imagebed/raw/master/alist_demo.webp" alt="Demo"></p><h2 id="1-Alist程序安装"><a href="#1-Alist程序安装" class="headerlink" title="1.Alist程序安装"></a>1.Alist程序安装</h2><p>为了使路径保持一致，在<code>docker</code>文件夹下，创建一个新文件夹命名为<code>alist</code>，在<code>alist</code>文件夹下，再创建一个新文件夹命名为<code>data</code>，用于存放数据库和配置文件。</p><h3 id="1-1命令行安装（推荐）"><a href="#1-1命令行安装（推荐）" class="headerlink" title="1.1命令行安装（推荐）"></a>1.1命令行安装（推荐）</h3><p>使用SSH工具登录群晖，并切换至root权限。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo -i</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="稳定版"><a href="#稳定版" class="headerlink" title="稳定版"></a>稳定版</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -d --restart=always -v /volume1/docker/alist/data:/opt/alist/data -p 5244:5244 --name=&quot;alist&quot; xhofe/alist:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="开发版"><a href="#开发版" class="headerlink" title="开发版"></a>开发版</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -d --restart=always -v /volume1/docker/alist/data:/opt/alist/data -p 5244:5244 --name=&quot;alist&quot; xhofe/alist:v2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>注意：</strong><code>/volume1/docker/alist/data</code>应根据具体路径进行设置。</p><h3 id="1-2docker管理器安装"><a href="#1-2docker管理器安装" class="headerlink" title="1.2docker管理器安装"></a>1.2docker管理器安装</h3><p>在注册表中搜索 <code>alist</code> ，选择 <code>xhofe/alist</code>lastest版本，双击直接下载。</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/holob/imagebed/raw/master/alist1.png" alt="下载镜像"></p><p>点击<code>映像</code>，双击刚刚下载的<code>xhofe/alist:latest</code>，开始创建容器。</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/holob/imagebed/raw/master/alist2.png" alt="创建容器"></p><p>点击<code>高级设置</code>，为了方便使用，勾选<code>启用自动重新启动</code>。</p><p>之后依次对存储空间和端口进行设置，装载路径为<code>/opt/alist/data</code>。</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/holob/imagebed/raw/master/alist6.png" alt="启用自动重新启动"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/holob/imagebed/raw/master/alist4.png" alt="端口设置"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/holob/imagebed/raw/master/alist5.png" alt="存储空间"></p><p>点击<code>应用</code>，再点击<code>下一步</code>，完成容器创建。</p><h2 id="2-Alist相关设置"><a href="#2-Alist相关设置" class="headerlink" title="2.Alist相关设置"></a>2.Alist相关设置</h2><p>在浏览器中输入 <code>http://群晖IP:5244</code>，输入初始密码<code>alist</code>，点击<code>登录</code>。</p><p>前端设置界面可以对站点标题、logo、头像等内容进行设置。</p><h3 id="自定义body"><a href="#自定义body" class="headerlink" title="自定义body"></a>自定义body</h3><p>显示站点运行时间（自用）</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;chakra-stack css-owjkmg&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;chakra-stack line0 css-g9cw6v&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span>本站已经运行<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;days&quot;</span>&gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span>天<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"><span class="keyword">var</span> s1 = <span class="string">&#x27;2022-01-15&#x27;</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">s1 = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Date</span>(s1.replace(<span class="regexp">/-/g</span>, <span class="string">&quot;/&quot;</span>));</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript">s2 = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Date</span>();</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"><span class="keyword">var</span> days = s2.getTime() - s1.getTime();</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"><span class="keyword">var</span> number_of_days = <span class="built_in">parseInt</span>(days / (<span class="number">1000</span> * <span class="number">60</span> * <span class="number">60</span> * <span class="number">24</span>));</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"><span class="built_in">document</span>.getElementById(<span class="string">&#x27;days&#x27;</span>).innerHTML = number_of_days;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-Alist添加账号"><a href="#3-Alist添加账号" class="headerlink" title="3.Alist添加账号"></a>3.Alist添加账号</h2><p>支持本地存储和十余种网络存储，添加账号具体方法参照<a href="https://alist-doc.nn.ci/docs/driver/base">官方文档</a>。</p><p><strong>注意：</strong>排序方向<code>asc</code>为正序，<code>desc</code>为倒序。</p><h2 id="4-Alist程序更新"><a href="#4-Alist程序更新" class="headerlink" title="4.Alist程序更新"></a>4.Alist程序更新</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker container ls  #获取容器ID</span><br><span class="line">docker stop containerID  #停止指定容器</span><br><span class="line">docker rm  containerID  #清除指定容器</span><br><span class="line">docker pull xhofe/alist:latest  #拉取最新镜像</span><br><span class="line">docker run -d --restart=always -v /volume1/docker/alist/data:/opt/alist/data -p 5244:5244 --name=&quot;alist&quot; xhofe/alist:latest  #运行镜像</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>（可选）</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker images  #获取镜像ID</span><br><span class="line">docker rmi imageID  #删除指定镜像</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="5-本地存储挂载"><a href="#5-本地存储挂载" class="headerlink" title="5.本地存储挂载"></a>5.本地存储挂载</h2><p>根目录路径应为容器内路径，挂载根目录用<code>/</code>，挂载指定文件夹，例如<code>/opt/alist/data</code>。</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/holob/imagebed/raw/master/alist7.png" alt="本地存储挂载"></p>]]></content>
      
      
